                "PROPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "Angular distributions for the alpha-particles",
                "scattered from 132,134,136,138Ba were measured between",
                "laboratory scattering angles of 25 and 115 degr. using",
                "an Enge split-pole spectrograph with a position-",
                "sensitive gas-filled proportional counter at the focal",
                "plane."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "The counts in the elastically scattered peak of",
                "the isotope under investigation were monitored with a",
                "silicon surface-barrier detector fixed at 90 degr."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Isotopically enriched targets of BaCl2 evaporated onto",
                "thin carbon backing.",
                "Isotopic abundances (%) of barium targets",
                "Isotope    Target",
                "           132Ba      134Ba      136Ba      138Ba",
